{"type":"message","id":"1a836d49","parentId":"a6a455cd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:29:45.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `LicenseCategory` type has both `id` and `code`. The backend's `create` endpoint expects `code`, not `id`. Looking at the backend service:\n\n```ts\nasync create(data: any): Promise<any> {\n  const doc = await LicenseCategoryModel.create({\n    name: data.name,\n    code: data.code || data.name,  // falls back to data.name\n    description: data.description || '',\n  });\n```\n\nThe backend accepts `code` and falls back to `data.name`. But the frontend modal is sending `id` (which is now the auto-generated code), not `code`. The `handleSave` function sends:\n\n\nThe modal is spreading `id`, `name`, `type`, `fee`, and other fields, but it's mapping `id` from `autoCode` when creating. I need to either rename `id` to `code` in the modal or add `code: autoCode` to the save payload. Looking at the backend's `findAll` response, it returns `code` from the DB, but the update endpoint also expects `code` in the request body.\n\nChecking the BE more carefully, the `create` method falls back to `data.name` if `code` is undefined, so it would work even if I only send `id`. But it's cleaner to explicitly send `code: autoCode` instead, since that's what the backend is looking for. Let me update the save handler to include that. I'm realizing the simplest approach is to just add the `code` field directly in the save handler when creating a new item, since the `LicenseCategory` interface supports it anyway. Let me update that.","thinkingSignature":"7eccc905873ff270f25431bfb1385523abc08f8092b62b7554c7b3f217074761"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5zwdwkr6dp1m_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/SettingsModals.tsx","edits":[{"oldText":"      await onSave({\n        id: item ? formData.id : autoCode,\n        name: formData.name,\n        type: formData.type,\n        fee: formattedFee,\n        tags: selectedTags,\n        inactive,\n        dat: formData.dat || null\n      });","newText":"      await onSave({\n        id: item ? formData.id : autoCode,\n        code: item ? formData.id : autoCode,\n        name: formData.name,\n        type: formData.type,\n        fee: formattedFee,\n        tags: selectedTags,\n        inactive,\n        dat: formData.dat || null\n      });"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":249,"output":563,"cacheRead":41713,"cacheWrite":402,"totalTokens":42927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776054576999,"responseId":"062ba43247f8ec77103fbc84691ae55e"}}
