{"type":"message","id":"9489415a","parentId":"b7285d7a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:48:47.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The remote develop is at `a8cf208` which is the merge of my MR. But my fix commit `8547471` (which contains the type fix) is NOT on develop yet! I pushed to `fix/auth-registration-ui`, not to `develop`. The `develop` branch still has the old code that fails the build.\n\nI need to merge my fix into develop. Let me:\n1. Merge fix/auth-registration-ui into develop\n2. Push develop\n\nOr alternatively, I can merge origin/fix/auth-registration-ui into develop.Wait - but the merge commit `a8cf208` was supposed to merge my MR (fix/auth-registration-ui) into develop. But the MR only included commits up to `bcd486d`. My latest fix commit `8547471` was pushed AFTER the MR was merged, so it's not in develop yet.\n\n\nNow I'll merge my fix branch into develop and push the updated code.","thinkingSignature":"e717083452e7aa1b50acde8baa72a05cb61c987c09e40d073087f278b7ca6887"},{"type":"text","text":"My fix commit chưa lên `develop`! MR đã merge trước khi mình push fix. Cần merge fix vào develop ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qkgi7c70w520_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe && git checkout develop && git merge origin/develop && git merge origin/fix/auth-registration-ui --no-edit && git push origin develop 2>&1 | tail -10","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":164,"output":324,"cacheRead":65114,"cacheWrite":1044,"totalTokens":66646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776055720524,"responseId":"062ba8a94fa448eb8a002be75184db2e"}}
