{"type":"message","id":"a1562da6","parentId":"3bd1d43b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:03:20.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The FE's `.env.local` is pointing to `http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1` but the backend is running locally on `localhost:5002`. So the FE is calling the remote server, but the remote server might not have the `/api/v1/license-categories` route deployed yet!\n\nActually wait - the issue might be that the backend on the remote server (103.253.21.139) doesn't have the latest code with the license-categories route. Let me check the backend route file to see if it's deployed.\n\nActually, I think the issue is simpler: the FE is calling the remote BE at `http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1/license-categories`, but the remote BE server might not have the `license-category.routes.ts` file deployed, OR the route path doesn't match.\n\n\nLet me verify whether the BE codebase actually includes the license-categories route in its routes configuration.","thinkingSignature":"6df93b57728f97ad680d6478e54181319c0afca0de7352a95e637678524d429f"},{"type":"text","text":"FE gọi remote BE: `http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1` — nhưng remote BE chưa có route `license-categories`!\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwukuhkod95a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1/license-categories 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":143,"output":299,"cacheRead":96190,"cacheWrite":455,"totalTokens":97087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056592211,"responseId":"062bac115a460ba128cfcacc75f0c2d0"}}
