{"type":"message","id":"45a5e976","parentId":"b7e37166","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:06:12.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No docker container running for the frontend. The docker-compose deploy only runs on the GitLab CI/CD runner (remote server). So I can't check the docker-compose config here.\n\nThe issue is clear: the deployed FE is calling port 8686, but the BE runs on port 5002. The `.env.local` has the correct URL with port 5002, but the CI/CD build might not have picked it up, OR the docker-compose on the deployment server has a wrong env file.\n\nActually wait - the `.env.local` is in the `.gitignore` and is not pushed to GitLab! That's the real problem. \n\nSo when the CI/CD pipeline runs `docker compose up -d --build`, it pulls the code from GitLab without `.env.local`, and the `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` falls back to the default `http://127.0.0.1:5002/api/v1` - which gets baked into the Docker image as a hardcoded value. The solution would be to either set up a proper `.env.production` file that gets committed to the repository, or pass the environment variable directly through the CI/CD pipeline.\n\nLooking at the error URL `http://103.253.21.139:8686/api/v1/license-categories`, the port is 8686, not 5002. This suggests either the production environment has a different `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` setting than expected, or the `next.config.ts` is being used to override the API URL with a hardcoded value. I need to trace where 8686 is actually coming from since it's not the standard backend port.\n\nThe most likely scenario is that the deployed container has a different environment variable set for `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` than what's in the local development setup. Rather than guessing at the configuration, I should suggest creating a `.env.production` file or passing the correct environment variable through the Docker compose setup, since that's the standard way to handle this in production deployments.","thinkingSignature":"515c3fb171cae9d9f2d692119bfc1e94b55254fa2210edd7ac0b9986dbc2b332"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra nguyên nhân rồi! \n\n**Port 8686 ≠ port 5002** — Backend đang chạy `:5002` nhưng FE gọi `:8686`.\n\nLý do: file `.env.local` có `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1` nhưng **`.env.local` nằm trong `.gitignore`**, không bao giờ được push lên GitLab → CI build không thấy → dùng fallback sai.\n\n**Cách fix — tạo `.env.production` được commit lên GitLab:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4ku4k8drwakh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"env\" .gitignore 2>/dev/null","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":711,"output":620,"cacheRead":98929,"cacheWrite":924,"totalTokens":101184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056757928,"responseId":"062bacb798bf7a3b4380aa57b2702b46"}}
