{"type":"compaction","id":"36ea0bec","parentId":"17361d07","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:19:38.459Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Fix 404 error on `/api/v1/license-categories` endpoint in the AHV QLHV system — caused by BE remote not having the `license-categories` API deployed\n2. Maintain clean git workflow: feature branches → MR → Lead review → Lead merge (never direct push to `develop`)\n3. Keep SOUL.md / MEMORY.md updated with operational rules\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- **NEVER push directly to `develop`** — always use feature branch + MR\n- **Lead reviews then merges** — agent does not self-merge\n- **Always `git fetch origin && git log origin/develop -3`** before each task\n- **Always `git merge origin/develop`** before push\n- **Always use `yarn` instead of `npm`**\n- **Never commit `.env.*` files** with secrets — `.env.local` is in `.gitignore`; `.env.production` was committed by mistake and IMMEDIATELY reverted\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Started BE (`yarn dev`) on port 5002 and FE (`yarn dev`) on port 3000 locally\n- [x] Fixed TypeScript `LicenseCategory` type mismatch between `settingsService.ts` (had `type: string`) and `licenseCategoryService.ts` (had `type: 'Ô tô' | 'Xe máy'`) — added `code: string` and aligned `type` and `dat` fields; build passed\n- [x] Committed/pushed fix to `origin/develop` on FE → CI pipeline passed (ID: 2448041411, status: success)\n- [x] **Reverted** direct push to `develop` on FE — pushed `.env.production` was a security mistake; immediately reverted with `git revert`\n- [x] Created feature branch `fix/api-url-env-production` for the env fix (on FE)\n- [x] Established feature branch workflow in SOUL.md (RULE 3: Git Sync + workflow rules)\n- [x] **Fixed** `require()` → ES module import in `exam.repository.ts` line 35 and 149 (`const { CourseStudentModel } = require(...)` → `import` at top); lint now passes 0 errors\n- [x] **Closed** MR #6 (notification) on BE — already merged into `develop` via MR #8 (`feat/student-import-background`)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **MR #7 BE** (`fix/auth-registration-bug` → `develop`) — awaiting CI pipeline pass\n  - Contains: `license-categories` CRUD API, auth defaults fix, notification system (merged from `develop`)\n  - Pipeline status: `pending` (GitLab runner `ahv-dtlx` was busy/offline)\n  - Merge status: `can_be_merged` (conflicts resolved)\n  - URL: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/merge_requests/7\n\n### Blocked\n- BE MR #7 pipeline stuck in `pending` — GitLab runner `ahv-dtlx` needs to be available/online to run CI jobs (lint + test stages)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **License modal reverted**: Initially auto-generated code from name, but Lead clarified `code` field should remain editable input (previous dev named it `id` causing confusion). Reverted to original behavior.\n- **`.env.production` never should have been committed**: Contains `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1`. Reverted immediately. The correct fix for the 404 was BE-side (push the `license-categories` API), not FE-side.\n- **BE workflow**: `fix/auth-registration-bug` branch contains 11 local commits (notification + license-categories) ahead of `origin/develop`; 2 commits from `origin/develop` (data isolation) merged in, creating one conflict resolved by keeping local notification system.\n- **MR #6 closed**: Notification content already merged into `develop` via MR #8 — no duplicate merge needed.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Wait for runner** on BE server → MR #7 CI pipeline to complete → Lead to merge MR #7 into `develop` → BE auto-deploys → 404 on `/api/v1/license-categories` will be resolved\n2. **FE MR for env fix** (`fix/api-url-env-production`) → Lead to review and merge (fixes `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` for deployment)\n3. **After MR #7 merge**: Re-sync local BE with remote develop, verify everything is consistent\n\n## Critical Context\n- **FE GitLab project**: `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (ID: 81078350) — token: `glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65`\n- **BE GitLab project**: `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (ID: 81078323) — same token\n- **Remote BE**: `http://103.253.21.139:5002` — currently running stale code (no `license-categories` API)\n- **Remote FE**: `http://103.253.21.139:3000` — deployed via `docker compose up -d --build` on CI runner\n- **Files modified**:\n  - `ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/settingsService.ts` — added `code: string` to `LicenseCategory` interface, aligned `type` and `dat` fields\n  - `ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/licenseCategoryService.ts` — `code` field made required\n  - `ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/repositories/exam.repository.ts` — converted `require()` to top-level `import`\n  - `ahv-qlhv-be/.gitlab-ci.yml` — removed `node_modules` from CI cache paths to fix stale cache issue\n- **SOUL.md** updated at: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md`\n- **MEMORY.md** updated at: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n## Original Request\nNo request — this is a system status heartbeat message from the Orbis-DTLX monitoring pipeline.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant recognized the message as a heartbeat\n- Responded with `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n## Context for Suffix\nNo suffix retained — the entire turn is shown above. The assistant acknowledged the status as informational only (no action required).\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/license-category.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/page.tsx\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/.gitlab-ci.yml\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/.env.production\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/SettingsModals.tsx\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/licenseCategoryService.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/settingsService.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"37d1c140","tokensBefore":157458,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/license-category.controller.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/page.tsx","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/MEMORY.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/.gitlab-ci.yml","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/.env.production","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/SettingsModals.tsx","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/licenseCategoryService.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/settingsService.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md"]},"fromHook":false}
