{"type":"message","id":"1b34293e","parentId":"f47921e4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:34:44.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants a professional finance-style UI for the tuition/fee page. This is a FE design task. I should spawn the `ui-ux-pro-max` or `ui-design-system` agent to handle this. Let me check what the current tuition page looks like first, then spawn the right agent.\n\nActually, based on the skill system, I should use `prompt-optimizer` first before spawning any agent. Let me think about this.\n\nThe request is about FE design/UI work. The most appropriate agents would be:\n- `ui-ux-pro-max` - UI/UX expert\n- `shadcn-expert` - component implementation\n\n\n- `ui-design-system` - design system\n\nSince this involves both design vision and implementation with shadcn/ui components, I need to start with `prompt-optimizer` to refine the requirements before triggering the right agent.","thinkingSignature":"cfbf7123468a0efb6a786c1f25769a6ba5c7b5b63ecfcb185e4193ed0a60a0dc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o7jw5uxjtt0e_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Design and implement a professional finance-style tuition/fee management page for the AHV QLHV system.\n\n## Context\n- Project: ahv-qlhv-fe (Next.js + shadcn/ui + Tailwind)\n- Existing tuition page: `src/app/tuition/page.tsx` or similar\n- Component library: shadcn/ui (already installed)\n- Design goal: Professional like finance websites (banks, fintech apps)\n\n## Design Requirements\n- **Style**: Professional finance/fintech aesthetic — clean, data-rich, trustworthy\n- **Color palette**: Deep blues, clean whites, subtle greens for positive values, reds for warnings\n- **Typography**: Clean sans-serif, clear hierarchy, numbers should be prominent and readable\n- **Layout**: Card-based dashboard showing fee summary, student fee list with filters, payment status indicators\n- **Components to include**:\n  - Summary cards (total revenue, pending payments, paid, overdue)\n  - Data table with sortable columns, pagination, search/filter\n  - Status badges (Đã đóng, Chưa đóng, Quá hạn)\n  - Export functionality (CSV/Excel)\n  - Date range filter\n  - Individual student fee detail modal\n\n## Steps\n1. Read the current tuition page at `src/app/tuition/page.tsx` (or find the actual path)\n2. Read the existing fee-related API services (`src/services/feeService.ts` or similar)\n3. Read shadcn/ui components available in the project\n4. Design and implement the professional tuition page\n5. Ensure responsive design (mobile-friendly)\n6. Test: `yarn lint` and `yarn build` must pass\n\n## Git Workflow\n- Create branch: `git checkout -b feat/tuition-page-finance-style origin/develop`\n- Commit: `git add . && git commit -m \"feat(tuition): redesign page with professional finance aesthetic\"`\n- Push: `git push origin feat/tuition-page-finance-style`\n- Create MR targeting `develop`\n\n## Output\n- Professional tuition page matching finance website aesthetics\n- All lint/build checks passing\n- MR link posted to group chat","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"ui-ux-pro-max","label":"ahv-qlhv-fe:ui-ux-pro-max:tuition-finance","mode":"session"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":3077,"output":708,"cacheRead":10789,"cacheWrite":30778,"totalTokens":45352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776069247219,"responseId":"062bdd811a4fc390e68026d3228847d1"}}
