{"type":"message","id":"08892ca0","parentId":"ec0057c6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:35:10.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Thread binding not available. Let me use `mode=run` instead for a one-shot task.","thinkingSignature":"afd1f068e679eddf5680328f64a303b88111d2c83e7b3864f242ea5c2d0999e9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n59uiv5yknug_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Design and implement a professional finance-style tuition/fee management page for the AHV QLHV system.\n\n## Context\n- Project: ahv-qlhv-fe (Next.js + shadcn/ui + Tailwind)\n- Workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe\n- Design goal: Professional like finance websites (banks, fintech apps)\n\n## Design Requirements\n- **Style**: Professional finance/fintech aesthetic — clean, data-rich, trustworthy\n- **Color palette**: Deep blues, clean whites, subtle greens for positive values, reds for warnings\n- **Typography**: Clean sans-serif, clear hierarchy, numbers prominent and readable\n- **Layout**: Card-based dashboard with summary stats + student fee table + filters\n- **Components**:\n  - Summary cards (total, paid, pending, overdue)\n  - Data table with sort/pagination/search\n  - Status badges (Đã đóng / Chưa đóng / Quá hạn)\n  - Export CSV\n  - Date range filter\n  - Student fee detail modal\n\n## Steps\n1. Find current tuition/fee page in the project\n2. Find fee-related API service\n3. Read shadcn/ui components available\n4. Implement the redesign\n5. `yarn lint` + `yarn build` must pass\n6. `git checkout -b feat/tuition-page-finance-style origin/develop`\n7. Commit + push + create MR → develop\n\n## Output\nPost MR link in the session when done.","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"ui-ux-pro-max","label":"ahv-qlhv-fe:ui-ux-pro-max:tuition-finance","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":189,"output":431,"cacheR