{"type":"message","id":"f5eb60b3","parentId":"1b9e4b0f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:37:46.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent failed due to gateway closure. The result shows the project structure but no actual work was done. The tuition page exists at `src/app/tuition/`. Let me spawn a new agent to do the actual work directly.","thinkingSignature":"16d56373dcb23a1143d17d97888b0b9146158ac957be3b7b7a91737b77b5b608"},{"type":"text","text":"Subagent bị gateway đóng — chạy lại:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3pea3q8ctnhk_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are working in workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe\n\n## Mission\nRedesign the tuition page to look like a professional finance/banking app.\n\n## Step 1: Find current files\nRun: `ls src/app/tuition/`\n\n## Step 2: Read the current tuition page code\n\n## Step 3: Check fee service\nRun: `find src/services -name \"*fee*\" -o -name \"*tuition*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10`\n\n## Step 4: Read shadcn table/card components\nRun: `ls src/components/ui/ | grep -E \"table|card|data-table|badge|button|input|select|tabs|chart\"`\n\n## Step 5: Implement redesign\nCreate a professional finance-style tuition page at `src/app/tuition/page.tsx`:\n\n```tsx\n// Professional Finance Dashboard Layout\n// - Dark blue header with summary stats\n// - 4 KPI cards: Tổng thu, Đã thu, Chưa thu, Quá hạn\n// - Search + date range filter bar\n// - Data table with: STT, Học viên, Khóa học, Số tiền, Trạng thái, Hạn nộp\n// - Status badges: Xanh (đã đóng), Vàng (chờ), Đỏ (quá hạn)\n// - Pagination\n// - Export CSV button\n```\n\nRequirements:\n- Use existing shadcn/ui components (Table, Badge, Card, Button, Input, Select)\n- Tailwind classes: bg-slate-900 text-white for header, bg-white cards\n- Real data from fee service (or mock if not available)\n- `yarn lint` and `yarn build` must pass\n\n## Step 6: Git workflow\n```\ngit fetch origin && git checkout -b feat/tuition-page-finance-style origin/develop\ngit add src/app/tuition/page.tsx\ngit commit -m \"feat(tuition): redesign with professional finance dashboard style\"\ngit push origin feat/tuition-page-finance-style\n```\n\n## Step 7: Create MR via GitLab API\n```\nPOST https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/81078350/merge_requests\ntitle: \"feat(tuition): redesign with professional finance dashboard style\"\nsource_branch: feat/tuition-page-finance-style\ntarget_branch: develop\n```\n\n## Step 8: Post the MR URL to the group chat","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"ui-ux-pro-max","label":"ahv-qlhv-fe:ui-ux-pro-max:tuition-redesign-v2","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":245,"output":685,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":43225,"totalTokens":44155,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776069446104,"responseId":"062bde47516f305e5f2f593737d30b49"}}
