{"type":"message","id":"03e03715","parentId":"4a9424d6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:18.100Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m94t8nof82mg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client';\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useCallback } from 'react';\nimport { Download, Plus } from 'lucide-react';\nimport { toast } from 'sonner';\nimport { getPayments, getPaymentStats, exportPayments } from '@/src/services/paymentService';\nimport TuitionSummaryCards from '@/src/components/tuition/TuitionSummaryCards';\nimport TuitionFilters, { TuitionFiltersState } from '@/src/components/tuition/TuitionFilters';\nimport TuitionTable from '@/src/components/tuition/TuitionTable';\nimport TuitionDetailModal from '@/src/components/tuition/TuitionDetailModal';\nimport AddPaymentModal from '@/src/components/tuition/AddPaymentModal';\nimport StudentDetailDrawer from '@/src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer';\nimport { useAuth } from '@/src/context/AuthContext';\n\nconst LIMIT = 20;\n\nexport default function TuitionPage() {\n  const { user } = useAuth();\n  const [filters, setFilters] = useState<TuitionFiltersState>({\n    search: '',\n    status: '',\n    dateFrom: '',\n    dateTo: '',\n  });\n  const [payments, setPayments] = useState<any[]>([]);\n  const [meta, setMeta] = useState<any>(null);\n  const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = useState(1);\n  const [stats, setStats] = useState({\n    total_received: 0,\n    total_receivable: 0,\n    total_debt: 0,\n    debtor_count: 0,\n  });\n  const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);\n  const [isExporting, setIsExporting] = useState(false);\n\n  // Modal/drawer state\n  const [detailItem, setDetailItem] = useState<any>(null);\n  const [isDetailModalOpen, setIsDetailModalOpen] = useState(false);\n  const [isAddPaymentModalOpen, setIsAddPaymentModalOpen] = useState(false);\n  const [selectedStudent, setSelectedStudent] = useState<any>(null);\n\n  const fetchPayments = useCallback(async (page = 1) => {\n    setIsLoading(true);\n    try {\n      const params: any = {\n        page,\n        limit: LIMIT,\n        search: filters.search,\n        status: filters.status,\n      };\n      if (filters.dateFrom) params.date_from = filters.dateFrom;\n      if (filters.dateTo) params.date_to = filters.dateTo;\n\n      const [res, statsRes] = await Promise.all([\n        getPayments(page, LIMIT, params),\n        getPaymentStats(),\n      ]);\n\n      if (res.success && res.data) {\n        setPayments(res.data.items || res.data.docs || res.data.data || []);\n        setMeta(res.data.pagination || res.data.meta);\n      }\n\n      if (statsRes.success && statsRes.data) {\n        setStats(statsRes.data);\n      }\n    } catch (error: any) {\n      toast.error('Lỗi khi tải dữ liệu học phí');\n    } finally {\n      setIsLoading(false);\n    }\n  }, [filters]);\n\n  // Fetch on page / filter change\n  useEffect(() => {\n    fetchPayments(currentPage);\n  }, [currentPage]);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (currentPage === 1) {\n      fetchPayments(1);\n    } else {\n      setCurrentPage(1);\n    }\n  }, [filters]);\n\n  // Refresh on payment events\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleRefresh = () => fetchPayments(1);\n    window.addEventListener('refresh-student-list', handleRefresh);\n    window.addEventListener('refresh-payment-list', handleRefresh);\n    return () => {\n      window.removeEventListener('refresh-student-list', handleRefresh);\n      window.removeEventListener('refresh-payment-list', handleRefresh);\n    };\n  }, [fetchPayments]);\n\n  const handleExport = async () => {\n    setIsExporting(true);\n    try {\n      await exportPayments(filters);\n      toast.success('Xuất dữ liệu Excel thành công');\n    } catch (error) {\n      toast.error('Lỗi khi xuất dữ liệu');\n    } finally {\n      setIsExporting(false);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const openDetailModal = (item: any) => {\n    setDetailItem(item);\n    setIsDetailModalOpen(true);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-5 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-2 duration-500\">\n\n      {/* Page header */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-baseline gap-4\">\n        <div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-1\">\n            <div className=\"w-1.5 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-indigo-600 rounded-full\" />\n            <h1 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight\">\n              Quản lý Học Phí\n            </h1>\n          </div>\n          <p className=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 ml-5\">\n            Theo dõi tình hình thu chi học phí &amp; công nợ\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 w-full sm:w-auto\">\n          <button\n            onClick={handleExport}\n            disabled={isExporting}\n            className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-all shadow-sm disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-sm\"\n          >\n            {isExporting ? (\n              <div className=\"w-4 h-4 border-2 border-slate-300 border-t-slate-600 rounded-full animate-spin\" />\n            ) : (\n              <Download className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            )}\n            Xuất CSV\n          </button>\n          <button\n            onClick={() => setIsAddPaymentModalOpen(true)}\n            className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 hover:bg-primary/90 active:scale-95 transition-all text-sm\"\n          >\n            <Plus className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            Thu tiền\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Summary cards */}\n      <TuitionSummaryCards\n        totalReceived={stats.total_received}\n        totalReceivable={stats.total_receivable}\n        totalDebt={stats.total_debt}\n        debtorCount={stats.debtor_count}\n        isLoading={isLoading}\n      />\n\n      {/* Filters */}\n      <TuitionFilters filters={filters} onChange={setFilters} isLoading={isLoading} />\n\n      {/* Table */}\n      <TuitionTable\n        payments={payments}\n        meta={meta}\n        currentPage={currentPage}\n        isLoading={isLoading}\n        onPageChange={setCurrentPage}\n        onViewDetail={openDetailModal}\n      />\n\n      {/* Detail modal */}\n      <TuitionDetailModal\n        item={detailItem}\n        onClose={() => {\n          setIsDetailModalOpen(false);\n          setDetailItem(null);\n        }}\n      />\n\n      {/* Add payment modal */}\n      <AddPaymentModal\n        isOpen={isAddPaymentModalOpen}\n        onClose={() => setIsAddPaymentModalOpen(false)}\n        onSuccess={() => fetchPayments(1)}\n      />\n\n      {/* Student detail drawer */}\n      <StudentDetailDrawer\n        isOpen={!!selectedStudent}\n        student={selectedStudent}\n        onClose={() => setSelectedStudent(null)}\n        defaultTab=\"hocphi\"\n      />\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776069797987}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e754328","parentId":"03e03715","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:18.245Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m94t8nof82mg_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"paymentService.ts"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":486,"aggregated":"paymentService.ts","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776069798100}}
{"type":"message","id":"49942874","parentId":"6e754328","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:43.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The tuition page already exists with quite a comprehensive design. Let me read the existing components to understand the current style and then suggest improvements to make it more finance/professional looking. Let me read the summary cards and table components.","thinkingSignature":"f1ebd62d7784cd5da06983f6f71959186b736a94251c210e36e042c2c8825230"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b27z3q4r4qoe_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/tuition/TuitionSummaryCards.tsx"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b27z3q4r4qoe_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/tuition/TuitionTable.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1811,"output":154,"cacheRead":44795,"cacheWrite":416,"totalTokens":47176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776069798251,"responseId":"062bdfa7efa841e078766e812db77f2d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e44535f2","parentId":"49942874","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:50.982Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_b27z3q4r4qoe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client';\n\nimport React from 'react';\nimport { DollarSign, TrendingUp, AlertTriangle, Users, CreditCard } from 'lucide-react';\n\ninterface TuitionSummaryCardsProps {\n  totalReceived: number;\n  totalReceivable: number;\n  totalDebt: number;\n  debtorCount: number;\n  isLoading?: boolean;\n}\n\nconst fmt = (n: number | undefined | null) =>\n  (n || 0).toLocaleString('vi-VN') + 'đ';\n\nfunction SkeletonCard() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm animate-pulse\">\n      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n        <div className=\"h-3 w-24 bg-slate-200 rounded\" />\n        <div className=\"h-10 w-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl\" />\n      </div>\n      <div className=\"h-8 w-36 bg-slate-200 rounded mb-2\" />\n      <div className=\"h-3 w-20 bg-slate-100 rounded\" />\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default function TuitionSummaryCards({\n  totalReceived,\n  totalReceivable,\n  totalDebt,\n  debtorCount,\n  isLoading = false,\n}: TuitionSummaryCardsProps) {\n  if (isLoading) {\n    return (\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        {Array.from({ length: 4 }).map((_, i) => (\n          <SkeletonCard key={i} />\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    );\n  }\n\n  const paid = totalReceived;\n  const pending = totalReceivable - totalReceived;\n  const collectionRate = totalReceivable > 0 ? Math.round((paid / totalReceivable) * 100) : 0;\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n      {/* Total Receivable — deep navy hero card */}\n      <div className=\"col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e3a8a] rounded-2xl p-6 text-white relative overflow-hidden min-h-[148px] flex flex-col justify-between\">\n        <div className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-10\">\n          <CreditCard className=\"w-24 h-24\" />\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"relative z-10\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n            <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white/60 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n              Tổng phải thu\n            </span>\n            <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm\">\n              <CreditCard className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/70\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-black text-white tabular-nums leading-none mb-2\">\n            {fmt(totalReceivable)}\n          </h3>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2\">\n          <div className=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-white/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n            <div\n              className=\"h-full bg-emerald-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-700\"\n              style={{ width: `${collectionRate}%` }}\n            />\n          </div>\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white/60 tabular-nums\">{collectionRate}%</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Collected / Paid */}\n      <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 min-h-[148px] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n            Đã thu\n          </span>\n          <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">\n            <TrendingUp className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-600\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 tabular-nums leading-none mb-1\">\n            {fmt(paid)}\n          </h3>\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-emerald-600\">\n            {collectionRate}% của tổng phải thu\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Pending / Unpaid */}\n      <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 min-h-[148px] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n            Chưa thu\n          </span>\n          <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">\n            <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-600\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-black text-amber-600 tabular-nums leading-none mb-1\">\n            {fmt(pending)}\n          </h3>\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-400\">\n            {totalReceivable - debtorCount > 0 ? `${totalReceivable - debtorCount} HV chưa đóng đủ` : 'Tất cả đã đóng đủ'}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Overdue / Debtor count */}\n      <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 min-h-[148px] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n            Quá hạn\n          </span>\n          <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-rose-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">\n            <Users className=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-600\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-black text-rose-600 tabular-nums leading-none mb-1\">\n            {fmt(totalDebt)}\n          </h3>\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-400\">\n            {debtorCount} học viên còn nợ\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776069830839}}
{"type":"message","id":"dbfd8487","parentId":"e44535f2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:51.148Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_b27z3q4r4qoe_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client';\n\nimport React, { useState } from 'react';\nimport {\n  ChevronUp,\n  ChevronDown,\n  ChevronsUpDown,\n  Eye,\n  ChevronLeft,\n  ChevronRight,\n  Loader2,\n} from 'lucide-react';\n\ntype SortKey = 'name' | 'paid' | 'total' | 'debt' | 'date' | 'status';\ntype SortDir = 'asc' | 'desc';\n\nconst fmt = (n: number | undefined | null) =>\n  (n || 0).toLocaleString('vi-VN') + 'đ';\n\ninterface PaymentItem {\n  _id: string;\n  received_fee?: number;\n  payment_date?: string;\n  is_tuition_account?: boolean;\n  course_student_id?: {\n    _id?: string;\n    fee?: number;\n    paid_fee?: number;\n    student_id?: {\n      _id?: string;\n      user_id?: {\n        _id?: string;\n        first_name?: string;\n        last_name?: string;\n        phone?: string;\n      };\n      region_id?: { name?: string };\n    };\n    course_id?: {\n      name?: string;\n      license_category_id?: { name?: string };\n    };\n  };\n}\n\ninterface TuitionTableProps {\n  payments: PaymentItem[];\n  meta: any;\n  currentPage: number;\n  isLoading?: boolean;\n  onPageChange: (page: number) => void;\n  onViewDetail: (item: PaymentItem) => void;\n}\n\nfunction StatusBadge({ debt, paid }: { debt: number; paid: number }) {\n  if (debt === 0) {\n    return (\n      <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-bold bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-200\">\n        <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\" />\n        Đã đóng\n      </span>\n    );\n  }\n  if (paid === 0) {\n    return (\n      <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-bold bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 border border-rose-200\">\n        <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-rose-500\" />\n        Quá hạn\n      </span>\n    );\n  }\n  return (\n    <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-bold bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border border-amber-200\">\n      <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500\" />\n      Đóng 1 phần\n    </span>\n  );\n}\n\nfunction SortIcon({ column, sortKey, sortDir }: { column: SortKey; sortKey: SortKey; sortDir: SortDir }) {\n  if (sortKey !== column) return <ChevronsUpDown className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-slate-300\" />;\n  return sortDir === 'asc'\n    ? <ChevronUp className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-primary\" />\n    : <ChevronDown className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-primary\" />;\n}\n\nexport default function TuitionTable({\n  payments,\n  meta,\n  currentPage,\n  isLoading = false,\n  onPageChange,\n  onViewDetail,\n}: TuitionTableProps) {\n  const [sortKey, setSortKey] = useState<SortKey>('date');\n  const [sortDir, setSortDir] = useState<SortDir>('desc');\n\n  const handleSort = (key: SortKey) => {\n    if (sortKey === key) {\n      setSortDir(d => (d === 'asc' ? 'desc' : 'asc'));\n    } else {\n      setSortKey(key);\n      setSortDir('desc');\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Build sortable rows\n  const rows: (PaymentItem & { _debt: number; _paid: number; _total: number; _name: string; _date: string })[] = payments.map(p => {\n    const cs = p.course_student_id || {};\n    const student = cs.student_id?.user_id || {};\n    const _paid = p.received_fee || cs.paid_fee || 0;\n    const _total = cs.fee || 0;\n    const _debt = _total - _paid;\n    const _name = `${student.last_name || ''} ${student.first_name || ''}`.trim() || 'Ẩn danh';\n    const _date = p.payment_date || '';\n    return { ...p, _debt, _paid, _total, _name, _date };\n  });\n\n  const sorted = [...rows].sort((a, b) => {\n    let cmp = 0;\n    switch (sortKey) {\n      case 'name': cmp = a._name.localeCompare(b._name); break;\n      case 'paid': cmp = a._paid - b._paid; break;\n      case 'total': cmp = a._total - b._total; break;\n      case 'debt': cmp = a._debt - b._debt; break;\n      case 'date': cmp = a._date.localeCompare(b._date); break;\n      case 'status':\n        if (a._debt === 0 && b._debt !== 0) cmp = -1;\n        else if (a._debt !== 0 && b._debt === 0) cmp = 1;\n        else cmp = a._paid - b._paid;\n        break;\n    }\n    return sortDir === 'asc' ? cmp : -cmp;\n  });\n\n  const totalPages = meta?.total_pages || 1;\n  const totalItems = meta?.total || 0;\n  const startItem = (currentPage - 1) * (meta?.limit || 20) + 1;\n  const endItem = Math.min(currentPage * (meta?.limit || 20), totalItems);\n\n  const thCls = (key: SortKey) =>\n    `px-4 py-3.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 cursor-pointer select-none hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap ${sortKey === key ? 'text-primary' : ''}`;\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n      <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n        <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse\">\n          <thead>\n            <tr className=\"bg-slate-50/80 border-b border-slate-100\">\n              <th className={thCls('name')} onClick={() => handleSort('name')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Học viên\n                  <SortIcon column=\"name\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap\">\n                Mã phiếu\n              </th>\n              <th className={thCls('paid')} onClick={() => handleSort('paid')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Đã đóng\n                  <SortIcon column=\"paid\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className={thCls('total')} onClick={() => handleSort('total')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Tổng phí\n                  <SortIcon column=\"total\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className={thCls('debt')} onClick={() => handleSort('debt')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Còn nợ\n                  <SortIcon column=\"debt\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className={thCls('date')} onClick={() => handleSort('date')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Ngày thu\n                  <SortIcon column=\"date\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className={thCls('status')} onClick={() => handleSort('status')}>\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  Trạng thái\n                  <SortIcon column=\"status\" sortKey={sortKey} sortDir={sortDir} />\n                </span>\n              </th>\n              <th className=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 text-right\">\n                Thao tác\n              </th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-slate-50\">\n            {isLoading ? (\n              Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (\n                <tr key={i}>\n                  {Array.from({ length: 8 }).map((_, j) => (\n                    <td key={j} className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <div className=\"h-4 bg-slate-100 rounded animate-pulse\" style={{ width: `${60 + Math.random() * 40}%` }} />\n                    </td>\n                  ))}\n                </tr>\n              ))\n            ) : sorted.length === 0 ? (\n              <tr>\n                <td colSpan={8} className=\"px-4 py-20 text-center\">\n                  <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-2\">\n                    <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xl\">📋</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400\">Không tìm thấy kết quả phù hợp</p>\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            ) : (\n              sorted.map((item) => {\n                const code = item.is_tuition_account\n                  ? 'ACC-' + item._id.slice(-6).toUpperCase()\n                  : item._id.slice(-6).toUpperCase();\n                const phone = item.course_student_id?.student_id?.user_id?.phone || '--';\n                const courseName = item.course_student_id?.course_id?.name || 'B2';\n\n                return (\n                  <tr\n                    key={item._id}\n                    className=\"hover:bg-slate-50/60 transition-colors group\"\n                  >\n                    {/* Student name + course */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4 min-w-[160px]\">\n                      <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-sm text-slate-900\">{item._name}</span>\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mt-0.5\">\n                          <span className=\"px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-[10px] font-bold border border-blue-100 rounded\">\n                            {courseName}\n                          </span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400\">{phone}</span>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Code */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <span className=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-lg\">\n                        #{code}\n                      </span>\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Paid */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <span className=\"font-bold text-sm text-emerald-600 tabular-nums\">\n                        {fmt(item._paid)}\n                      </span>\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Total */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <span className=\"font-semibold text-sm text-slate-700 tabular-nums\">\n                        {fmt(item._total)}\n                      </span>\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Debt */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      {item._debt > 0 ? (\n                        <span className=\"font-bold text-sm text-rose-600 tabular-nums\">\n                          {fmt(item._debt)}\n                        </span>\n                      ) : (\n                        <span className=\"text-emerald-500 text-sm font-bold\">—</span>\n                      )}\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Date */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\">\n                        {item._date\n                          ? new Date(item._date).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN')\n                          : '--'}\n                      </span>\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Status */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4\">\n                      <StatusBadge debt={item._debt} paid={item._paid} />\n                    </td>\n\n                    {/* Actions */}\n                    <td className=\"px-4 py-4 text-right\">\n                      <button\n                        onClick={() => onViewDetail(item)}\n                        title=\"Xem chi tiết\"\n                        className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all rounded-lg font-semibold text-[11px] shadow-sm group/btn\"\n                      >\n                        <Eye className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover/btn:scale-110 transition-transform\" />\n                        Chi tiết\n                      </button>\n                    </td>\n                  </tr>\n                );\n              })\n            )}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Pagination */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 border-t border-slate-100 gap-3\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-0.5\">\n          <span className=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-500\">\n            {isLoading ? 'Đang tải…' : (\n              <>\n                Hiển thị <strong className=\"text-slate-900\">{endItem > 0 ? startItem : 0}–{endItem}</strong> trong{' '}\n                <strong className=\"text-slate-900\">{totalItems}</strong> phiếu\n              </>\n            )}\n          </span>\n          {!isLoading && totalItems > 0 && (\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-400\">Tổng thu:</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[11px] font-black text-emerald-600 tabular-nums\">\n                {fmt(rows.reduce((s, r) => s + r._paid, 0))}\n              </span>\n              <span className=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-400\">· Tổng nợ:</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[11px] font-black text-rose-600 tabular-nums\">\n                {fmt(rows.reduce((s, r) => s + r._debt, 0))}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n          <button\n            onClick={() => onPageChange(Math.max(1, currentPage - 1))}\n            disabled={currentPage === 1 || isLoading}\n            className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-all\"\n          >\n            <ChevronLeft className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n            Trước\n          </button>\n\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl\">\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-black text-primary\">{currentPage}</span>\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\">/</span>\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500\">{totalPages}</span>\n          </div>\n\n          <button\n            onClick={() => onPageChange(Math.min(totalPages, currentPage + 1))}\n            disabled={currentPage === totalPages || isLoading}\n            className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-all\"\n          >\n            Sau\n            <ChevronRight className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n          </button>\n\n          {isLoading && <Loader2 className=\"w-4 h-4 animate-spin text-slate-400 ml-1\" />}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776069830988}}
{"type":"message","id":"78d11322","parentId":"dbfd8487","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:44:14.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current tuition page is actually already quite well-designed! It has:\n- Summary cards with gradient dark navy hero card\n- Professional color palette (emerald for paid, amber for pending, rose for overdue)\n- Sortable table with status badges\n- Pagination\n- Export functionality\n\nLead wants it to look even MORE like finance websites. The current design is already decent, but I can suggest specific improvements to make it more \"finance app\" like. Let me share an honest assessment with Lead.\n\nActually, looking at it again, the current design is already quite professional and finance-style. Maybe Lead hasn't seen it yet and wants to confirm the design. Or maybe they want specific additional features like:\n\n\n- Charts/graphs\n- More premium card styling\n- Better typography\n- A timeline view for payment history\n- PDF receipts\n- Better mobile layout\n\nI should report back to Lead what the current design actually looks like and ask what specific changes they're after.","thinkingSignature":"cc1e9befa963edb9919eb37cd8bdb42fe443c952bd0b269b7da48a2b96c594e1"},{"type":"text","text":"Trang học phí hiện tại đã có thiết kế khá chuyên nghiệp rồi ạ:\n\n**Hiện tại đã có:**\n- ✅ 4 KPI cards (Tổng phải thu / Đã thu / Chưa thu / Quá hạn) — gradient navy hero card\n- ✅ Bảng dữ liệu sortable, pagination, search/filter\n- ✅ Status badges màu (emerald=đã đóng, amber=chưa, rose=quá hạn)\n- ✅ Progress bar tỷ lệ thu\n- ✅ Export CSV\n- ✅ Modal chi tiết từng học viên\n- ✅ Nút \"Thu tiền\"\n\n**Lead muốn nâng cấp thêm phần nào?** Ví dụ:\n1. **Biểu đồ** — chart line/bar thu chi theo tháng\n2. **Receipt/PDF** — in phiếu thu đẹp như ngân hàng\n3. **Timeline** — lịch sử thanh toán của từng HV\n4. **So sánh** — thu chi tháng này vs tháng trước\n5. **Khác** — xin Lead mô tả cụ thể"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":5544,"output":505,"cacheRead":45022,"cacheWrite":2057,"totalTokens":53128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776069831157,"responseId":"062bdfc86a4d510511c3f122f5a75954"}}
