{"type":"message","id":"6c37e596","parentId":"569590a1","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:56:10.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Confirmed - there's NO `/auth/register` route in DTLX BE! This is a missing feature. The DTLX BE only has signin, change-password, and refetch-token.\n\nThis is a significant missing feature. I should report this to Lead and suggest building the registration endpoint.\n\nLet me also check the git status to see if there's a branch with registration work.","thinkingSignature":"37f425d842d48a7415d43bcc0b6639e0faf1199456ef8891ed1012e1e4bb9c2e"},{"type":"text","text":"**Tìm ra vấn đề rồi!** DTLX BE **thiếu hoàn toàn endpoint `/auth/register`**.\n\nChỉ có 3 routes auth:\n- `POST /signin` ✅\n- `PATCH /change-password` ✅\n- `POST /refetch-token` ✅\n- ❌ `/register` — KHÔNG TỒN TẠI\n- ❌ `/profile` — KHÔNG TỒN TẠI\n\nĐây là feature mới, cần xây dựng. Lead muốn mình xây `register` endpoint cho DTLX BE không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":516,"output":225,"cacheRead":72633,"cacheWrite":428,"totalTokens":73802,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776142563686,"responseId":"062cfbe5dfedd90f00826fec64df1855"}}
