{"type":"message","id":"d7b7c7ce","parentId":"3ec64b0c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T05:00:57.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The DTLX backend doesn't have its own git repo. It's just a directory in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace. Changes can't be committed directly. I need to report this fix to Lead and let them know where to apply it.\n\nActually wait — I can apply the fix to the source files. The files are already modified. The changes are:\n- `src/modules/auth/auth.controller.ts`: `user.user.id` → `user.user._id` (2 places)\n- `dist/modules/auth/auth.controller.js`: same fix\n\nThese are just local file edits. Since there's no git repo in the DTLX backend directory, I should just report the fix was applied and let the Lead/dtlx team know.","thinkingSignature":"d61d49d4cd563bc889820b0198ba1501062d591bcc5a96c3f29a5f0dbfdb7fb6"},{"type":"text","text":"**Fix đã apply!** Không có git repo riêng trong DTLX BE — chỉ là directory trong workspace.\n\n**Thay đổi đã thực hiện:**\n- `src/modules/auth/auth.controller.ts`: `user.user.id` → `user.user._id` (2 chỗ — dòng 30, 38)\n- `dist/.../auth.controller.js`: tương tự\n\n**Root cause:** Mongoose dùng `_id` là primary key, không phải `id`. Khi `.lean()` query → `doc.id` = `undefined` → JWT payload sai → 401.\n\n**Note:** DTLX BE thiếu `/auth/register` và `/profile` — Lead cần xây thêm endpoints này nếu cần."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":116,"output":333,"cacheRead":76219,"cacheWrite":271,"totalTokens":76939,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776142848039,"responseId":"062cfd01a87e3ae6d5c6649d238b001d"}}
